FT  03 DEC 92 / UK Company News: GEC edges ahead to Pounds 356m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
GEC REPORTED a 'notably strong' performance in its three main divisions for
the six months to September 30, though market conditions were not always
favourable. Several other of its businesses were hit by recessionary
conditions, however.
