improvements in ECGD cover will help us in our drive to win vital overseas
orders'.
On sales of Pounds 4.26bn (Pounds 4.49bn), pre-tax profits were Pounds 356m
(Pounds 346m). After tax of Pounds 119m (Pounds 117m) and minorities
