<TEXT>
MOUNTVIEW Estates, the property dealing group, reported a modest 2 per cent
increase in pre-tax profits from Pounds 3.54m to Pounds 3.62m in the half
year to September 30, as higher rental income offset its exposure to the
depressed south-east property market.
