FT  02 DEC 92 / Fiery protest
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Thousands of farmers from across Europe gather around a bonfire in the Place
de Bordeaux, Strasbourg, for a rally against the EC-US trade deal and farm
reforms. About 50,000 farmers took part in the demonstration yesterday,
which began in a festive atmosphere but was marred by sporadic violence
later as fireworks were thrown and police foiled an attempt to storm the
European Parliament.
